  "data": {
    "id": "",
    "status": "Active",
    "name": "Example Client",
    "product": "RedSeed Pro",
    "dateStarted": "2023-02-14T11:00:00.000000Z",
    "dateEngagement": null,
    "dateCreatedAt": "2023-02-14T19:52:57.000000Z",
    "dateUpdatedAt": "2023-02-14T19:52:57.000000Z"
  }
}
```
### URL endpoint
`
https://api.redseed.me/v0/clients/{UUID}
`
### URL Parameters

Parameter | Description
--------- | -----------
{UUID} | The UUID of the client resource

### URL Query Parameters

None

<aside class="notice">
You must replace <code>{UUID}</code> with the uuid of the client resource and <code>{MY_API_TOKEN}</code> with your personal API key.
</aside>

